513
00:53:11,945 --> 00:53:13,071
Leave Rishi...

514
00:53:17,150 --> 00:53:18,674
You don't love him...

515
00:53:23,557 --> 00:53:24,717
By being with him like this...

516
00:53:24,925 --> 00:53:27,416
