525
00:55:01,221 --> 00:55:02,688
Thank God I have you...

526
00:55:14,301 --> 00:55:15,768
chandigarh...

527
00:55:40,260 --> 00:55:43,388
We knew this was the end of our journey...

528
00:55:44,064 --> 00:55:47,659
These were the last few
breaths of our love story...

529
00:55:47,968 --> 00:55:49,799
We had to collect these moments...

530
00:55:50,036 --> 00:55:54,496
...and breathe a new life into
our old relationships...

531
00:55:54,841 --> 00:55:57,036
It was time to go home...

532
00:55:57,744 --> 00:56:01,145
We had to tell Rishi and Rhea the truth...

533
00:56:01,548 --> 00:56:06,008
Because happiness can never bloom
in the shadow of lies...

534
00:56:06,753 --> 00:56:09,153
No one knew this betterthan us...

535
00:57:11,351 --> 00:57:12,045
Rhea...

536
00:57:18,758 --> 00:57:23,218
There's another woman in my life...

537
00:57:24,364 --> 00:57:25,558
That's not funny anymore...

538
00:57:27,701 --> 00:57:28,998
I'm not joking...

539
00:57:33,039 --> 00:57:34,404
Forthe last six months...

540
00:57:39,379 --> 00:57:45,181
But it's over now...

541
00:57:47,520 --> 00:57:48,316
Maya...

542
00:57:53,626 --> 00:57:57,619
Why it happened... I don't have any answers...

543
00:58:04,571 --> 00:58:14,503
But I want to give our marriage
another chance...

544
00:58:17,650 --> 00:58:19,117
Do you love her?

545
00:58:22,489 --> 00:58:24,218
How does it matter?

546
00:58:26,960 --> 00:58:28,325
It matters to me...

547
00:58:35,502 --> 00:58:40,030
If I had to do what you did...
would you forgive me?

548
00:58:46,513 --> 00:58:50,745
You wouldn't, Dev...
You would neverforgive me...

549
00:59:08,568 --> 00:59:15,940
You will have to leave this house...
This marriage is over...

550
00:59:35,962 --> 00:59:39,261
Rishi... Listen to me...

551
00:59:41,067 --> 00:59:48,701
Listen to me... Rishi... Rishi...

552
00:59:57,250 --> 00:59:58,376
Did you sleep with him?

553
01:00:00,420 --> 01:00:05,915
You slept with him? Tell me, Maya...

554
01:00:07,093 --> 01:00:11,120
How was it? Was it fun?

555
01:00:11,331 --> 01:00:18,464
Did you have fun? Tell me...

556
01:00:21,074 --> 01:00:22,735
Tell me...

557
01:00:27,013 --> 01:00:31,473
How strange Maya, that you kept
cleaning this house all the time...

558
01:00:32,418 --> 01:00:35,080
...and today you have brought in so much filth...

559
01:00:35,355 --> 01:00:37,380
Don't say that, Rishi...
- Then what should I say?

560
01:00:39,526 --> 01:00:40,515
What should I do?

561
01:00:43,363 --> 01:00:44,523
Celebrate?

562
01:00:47,567 --> 01:00:52,834
Should I celebrate that my wife is
sleeping with another man?

563
01:01:00,113 --> 01:01:10,489
I'm sorry, Rishi... I'm sorry... I'm sorry...

564
01:01:10,690 --> 01:01:12,123
Why did you do this...

565
01:01:17,130 --> 01:01:19,462
Why did you do this to me, Maya?

566
01:01:24,304 --> 01:01:26,772
I loved you so much...

567
01:01:30,510 --> 01:01:32,205
More than my own self...

568
01:01:33,346 --> 01:01:34,836
More than life...

569
01:01:37,417 --> 01:01:42,980
But it wasn't enough foryou, right?

570
01:01:43,223 --> 01:01:44,053
It's not like that, Rishi...

571
01:01:44,257 --> 01:01:45,724
Then how is it, Maya?

572
01:01:53,733 --> 01:02:01,868
Every morning I woke up
to look into your eyes...

573
01:02:07,046 --> 01:02:08,843
To search for my face...

574
01:02:17,156 --> 01:02:19,283
But now I will only see him...

575
01:02:24,330 --> 01:02:30,030
