576
01:02:32,805 --> 01:02:35,296
But that relationship is over, Rishi...

577
01:02:38,645 --> 01:02:40,442
This relationship is over, Maya...

578
01:03:02,435 --> 01:03:03,902
Then I'll leave...?

579
01:03:08,875 --> 01:03:10,206
I won't stop you...

580
01:03:31,197 --> 01:03:32,926
Try not to hate me, Arjun...

581
01:03:48,748 --> 01:03:54,983
Rhea... I want to say something to you...

582
01:03:58,591 --> 01:04:01,992
Dev didn't ask me before stepping
out of this marriage...

583
01:04:02,995 --> 01:04:05,862
Neither did you ask me
before throwing him out...

584
01:04:06,733 --> 01:04:12,672
But my grandson's eyes ask me
whether I'm going to leave him...

585
01:04:15,842 --> 01:04:17,469
I can't do that, Rhea...

586
01:04:19,712 --> 01:04:21,771
So if you have no objections...

587
01:04:22,849 --> 01:04:24,942
I would like to stay with you...

588
01:04:27,120 --> 01:04:28,348
can I?

589
01:05:47,500 --> 01:05:52,665
Hello... hello...

590
01:05:56,375 --> 01:05:57,307
Dev...

591
01:05:59,479 --> 01:06:00,446
Maya...

592
01:06:00,880 --> 01:06:04,281
Yeah... Got dialled by mistake...

593
01:06:06,352 --> 01:06:07,649
Are you ok?

594
01:06:12,692 --> 01:06:16,287
Did you... Tell Rishi... Rishi?

595
01:06:16,496 --> 01:06:19,727
I told Rishi everything...

596
01:06:20,132 --> 01:06:21,622
What did he say?

597
01:06:21,834 --> 01:06:23,267
He was very angry at first...

598
01:06:23,836 --> 01:06:28,273
But with time I know he will forgive me...

599
01:06:29,775 --> 01:06:32,938
He's a good man...

600
01:06:36,182 --> 01:06:37,171
And Rhea?

601
01:06:38,317 --> 01:06:48,522
Even she will forgive me with time...
After all family is family...

602
01:06:49,061 --> 01:06:51,188
Yeah... Family is family...

603
01:06:55,868 --> 01:06:57,392
Yeah Rhea... I'm coming...

604
01:06:58,804 --> 01:07:02,501
Even I am at home... with Rishi...

605
01:07:04,877 --> 01:07:05,935
Be happy...

606
01:07:24,230 --> 01:07:25,288
Goodbye...

607
01:07:26,766 --> 01:07:30,725
All our relationships were
defined by this one word...

608
01:07:31,437 --> 01:07:35,737
Both of us left our homes and
didn't even tell each other about it...

609
01:07:36,876 --> 01:07:41,370
I had never seen the hope of meeting again...

610
01:07:41,581 --> 01:07:43,674
...die such a silent death before...

611
01:08:22,521 --> 01:08:27,823
Your heart knows...

612
01:08:28,828 --> 01:08:34,630
And so does mine...

613
01:08:35,334 --> 01:08:47,508
That our roads are meant to part...

614
01:08:48,114 --> 01:08:54,246
Far apart though we will be...

615
01:08:54,453 --> 01:09:00,050
