Hi, Good morning. - Hi Miss.

620
01:10:09,628 --> 01:10:15,692
My name is Maya Tal... My name is Maya.

621
01:10:16,869 --> 01:10:22,398
All the mirth in life has slipped away slowly...

622
01:10:22,875 --> 01:10:28,973
It's the pain that refuses to go away...

623
01:10:29,515 --> 01:10:35,476
Tried to wish it away...
tried to laugh it away...

624
01:10:35,888 --> 01:10:41,758
But the heart fails to find peace...

625
01:10:42,228 --> 01:10:44,628
