01:12:19,892 --> 01:12:25,922
But the season of pain is here to stay...

633
01:12:26,465 --> 01:12:32,301
The shade of sorrow is so deep...

634
01:12:32,738 --> 01:12:41,806
That it will take a while to pale...

635
01:12:42,014 --> 01:12:47,816
Who knows what's to happen ahead...

636
01:12:48,254 --> 01:12:53,988
Who knows what's in store for us to bear...

