650
01:14:55,447 --> 01:14:56,277
Thanks...

651
01:15:17,803 --> 01:15:21,534
Do you know Maya, that in these three
years, I tried hard to hate you...

652
01:15:22,641 --> 01:15:27,374
To forget you... but I couldn't...

653
01:15:30,649 --> 01:15:31,911
...couldn't do it, Maya...

654
01:15:36,155 --> 01:15:41,218
You gave up the house, but the house
could never give you up...

655
01:15:43,996 --> 01:15:47,557
You were right... I was a child...

656
01:15:47,933 --> 01:15:53,166
I could never understand you...
And that I realize today...

657
01:15:58,010 --> 01:15:59,307
I have grown up, Maya...

658
01:16:06,218 --> 01:16:07,810
I am in love again...

659
01:16:10,389 --> 01:16:11,754
I'm getting married...

660
01:16:16,795 --> 01:16:17,955
Won't you say anything?

661
01:16:24,369 --> 01:16:25,961
I'm very happy foryou...

662
01:16:33,979 --> 01:16:35,276
Her name is catherine...

663
01:16:41,253 --> 01:16:43,983
And I want you to be the best man
at my wedding, Maya...

664
01:16:53,832 --> 01:17:02,297
I don't have anyone besides you...
You are my family...

665
01:17:04,676 --> 01:17:09,443
Always have been... always will be...

666
01:17:24,496 --> 01:17:25,724
This is foryou.

667
01:17:30,169 --> 01:17:30,931
Dad!

668
01:17:38,210 --> 01:17:43,045
Wherever he is... he is with us...

669
01:17:51,056 --> 01:17:52,353
...he is with you...

670
01:18:07,773 --> 01:18:11,265
Jai... I'm not ready yet...

671
01:18:15,581 --> 01:18:18,049
I am being a motherto my
son after many years...

672
01:18:19,017 --> 01:18:24,546
At this point I'm happy with this
one relationship... And...

673
01:18:24,756 --> 01:18:27,657
You don't have to say anything...

674
01:18:28,760 --> 01:18:32,526
Ijust want you to know that
I'll be waiting... Ok?

675
01:18:35,667 --> 01:18:40,070
I'm sorry... Ijust came to say 'Bye'...

676
01:18:40,606 --> 01:18:43,302
Rhea... You just get ready...
I'll wait foryou outside...

677
01:18:45,577 --> 01:18:48,637
And good luck with your job in canada...

678
01:18:57,022 --> 01:18:58,546
What time is yourtrain?

679
01:19:00,392 --> 01:19:02,485
In two hours...

680
01:19:10,902 --> 01:19:11,527
Arjun...

681
01:19:11,737 --> 01:19:15,833
I know... I met Mom...

682
01:19:16,642 --> 01:19:18,837
He probably forgot that I was leaving today...

683
01:19:20,312 --> 01:19:27,081
Rhea... I have lost my right to
ask you forforgiveness...

684
01:19:30,989 --> 01:19:33,457
...but I don't want to lose the
right to bless you...

685
01:19:45,003 --> 01:19:46,698
Have a good life...

686
01:19:48,874 --> 01:19:50,068
You stay in touch...

687
