God! Rhea... We are really late...

688
01:20:09,861 --> 01:20:10,885
I'm so sorry, Jai...

689
01:20:11,096 --> 01:20:12,222
Don't worry about it...

690
01:20:14,666 --> 01:20:17,430
Jai... I'm going to kill you...
You missed the ceremony...

691
01:20:17,636 --> 01:20:19,934
Not my fault, sweetheart... Blame it on Rhea...

692
01:20:20,138 --> 01:20:21,435
congratulations...

693
01:20:21,640 --> 01:20:23,835
Rhea... It's so nice to finally meet you...

694
01:20:24,042 --> 01:20:25,634
Jai talks about you all the time...

695
01:20:25,844 --> 01:20:26,708
Well I hope good things...

696
01:20:26,912 --> 01:20:30,678
Of course... You haven't met
my husband... Sweetheart?

697
01:20:33,552 --> 01:20:35,520
Come meet my oldest friend
in the world... This is...

698
01:20:35,721 --> 01:20:37,484
Rhea... - Rishi?

699
01:20:37,689 --> 01:20:39,247
Great... You know each other?

700
01:20:40,359 --> 01:20:41,018
Yes... We do...

701
01:20:41,226 --> 01:20:43,194
congratulations... You are a lucky man...

702
01:20:43,395 --> 01:20:43,861
Thank you...

703
01:20:44,062 --> 01:20:45,495
Jai you are never going to
believe who's in town...

704
01:20:45,697 --> 01:20:47,858
Honey... we'll see you later... Rhea...

705
01:20:48,066 --> 01:20:48,760
See you in a bit...

706
01:20:51,236 --> 01:20:55,605
Rishi? Your wedding? What about Maya?

707
01:20:55,874 --> 01:20:58,900
Maya and I separated three years ago...

708
01:21:01,046 --> 01:21:04,413
And you here? With Jai?

709
01:21:04,883 --> 01:21:07,351
Dev and I divorced three years ago...

710
01:21:13,125 --> 01:21:18,062
But do Dev and Maya know this?

711
01:21:41,686 --> 01:21:51,084
Maya... What's the matter Maya?

712
01:21:51,797 --> 01:21:56,131
Can't look me in the eye... can't face me...

713
01:21:56,701 --> 01:22:01,832
Because you broke my heart? My home?

714
01:22:04,309 --> 01:22:06,539
How could you break something
that was already broken, Maya?

715
01:22:07,779 --> 01:22:12,682
Maybe you shouldn't have filled
the void between Dev and me...

716
01:22:14,453 --> 01:22:18,947
But what could you do?
Dev's love is like that...

717
01:22:20,559 --> 01:22:23,790
Ask me... I know...

718
01:22:24,596 --> 01:22:29,056
Don't be so large-hearted Rhea
that I feel even smaller...

719
01:22:29,267 --> 01:22:30,996
I'm not that magnanimous...

720
01:22:32,504 --> 01:22:36,873
When Dev told me about you I left him...

721
01:22:40,045 --> 01:22:42,013
But I don't think you know that...

722
01:22:47,319 --> 01:22:52,313
How strange!
The love that changed the destinies...

723
01:22:53,191 --> 01:22:55,819
...of two homes today stands destitute...

724
01:22:57,095 --> 01:23:00,553
I moved on... Rishi moved on...

725
01:23:01,766 --> 01:23:04,064
The two of you got left behind...

726
01:23:04,369 --> 01:23:05,996
Perhaps that's our punishment...

727
01:23:06,204 --> 01:23:07,728
Such a small punishment?

728
01:23:08,640 --> 01:23:13,270
Try living with Dev... Then you
will know what punishment is...

729
01:23:20,151 --> 01:23:21,914
Ok... I had to fight fifty women forthis...

730
01:23:23,488 --> 01:23:24,420
It's tradition...

731
01:23:26,258 --> 01:23:30,524
...the girl who gets these flowers
gets a new life...

732
01:23:32,063 --> 01:23:37,695
...new happiness... And I want
that girl to be you, Maya...

733
01:23:40,071 --> 01:23:42,369
Your heart has been searching
for love for many years...

734
01:23:44,676 --> 01:23:46,268
...and that love is Dev...

735
01:23:50,048 --> 01:23:55,543
And if you don't hurry now your love
will move further away from you...

736
01:23:56,421 --> 01:24:00,289
Dev is leaving for Toronto... His train
leaves in fifteen minutes...

737
01:24:08,099 --> 01:24:13,435
Go, Maya... Go get your love
before it's too late...

738
01:24:17,676 --> 01:24:18,574
Go...

739
01:24:27,319 --> 01:24:28,251
Thank you...

740
01:25:03,254 --> 01:25:03,913
And Rhea?

741
01:25:04,556 --> 01:25:08,492
Even she will forgive me with time...

742
01:27:15,019 --> 01:27:15,849
Maya!

743
01:27:22,293 --> 01:27:23,055
Dev...

744
01:27:32,303 --> 01:27:34,999
Aren't you a little overdressed forthe station?

745
01:27:35,373 --> 01:27:41,972
Sorry... It's been a while hasn't it?

746
01:27:43,481 --> 01:27:45,005
I don't live here anymore...

747
01:27:46,918 --> 01:27:49,409
And I don't live here despite being here...

748
01:27:50,255 --> 01:27:52,018
Watch where you are going!

749
01:27:53,291 --> 01:27:57,887
Nothing's changed Dev...
You still get angry at everything...

750
01:27:59,664 --> 01:28:06,331
Anger's my own... Doesn't leave me...
Love can always leave and go...

751
01:28:07,172 --> 01:28:09,868
What will you do if you find your lost love?

752
01:28:11,276 --> 01:28:17,806
What will I say now, Maya...
I'll just say 'go back'!

753
01:28:18,683 --> 01:28:26,180
Dev... Only I know how I have
survived these three years...

754
01:28:28,459 --> 01:28:32,486
There was not a moment in the
day when I didn't think of you...

755
01:28:35,600 --> 01:28:39,263
But I used to convince myself
that you are alright...

756
01:28:40,839 --> 01:28:44,331
...you are happy with yourfamily...

757
01:28:45,543 --> 01:28:47,374
I used to think of your happiness...

758
01:28:48,746 --> 01:28:51,237
...and it would reduce a bit
of my unhappiness...

759
01:28:54,052 --> 01:29:01,049
But today I realized that you
have been as alone as I am...

760
01:29:05,496 --> 01:29:06,360
Yes, Dev...

761
01:29:08,233 --> 01:29:12,966
Even I have been alone forthree years...

762
01:29:14,105 --> 01:29:16,073
Alone... Like you...

763
01:29:21,212 --> 01:29:22,270
Why, Dev?

764
01:29:23,748 --> 01:29:26,774
Why did all this happen? Why?

765
01:29:26,985 --> 01:29:34,892
Why did we meet? And then part?
Why, Dev? Why?

766
01:29:47,338 --> 01:29:49,329
Everyone shares happiness and sorrow...

767
01:29:50,775 --> 01:29:53,243
I want to share my punishment with you...

768
01:29:54,612 --> 01:29:57,911
My life may not be complete living with you...

769
01:29:58,116 --> 01:30:00,482
...but at least it will be a life...

770
01:30:02,553 --> 01:30:07,149
Will you share this incomplete
life with me, Maya...

771
01:30:11,496 --> 01:30:14,329
Answer me, Maya... It's hurting...

772
01:30:17,802 --> 01:30:20,771
Answer... I can't sit here the whole...

773
01:30:21,673 --> 01:30:23,903
What do you want me to do?
Go down on my knees?

774
01:30:24,409 --> 01:30:30,370
Shut up... Just shut up... Speak politely...

775
01:30:30,581 --> 01:30:36,577
Ok... Hello... Thank you... Nice to meet you...

776
01:30:37,055 --> 01:30:38,784
I love you... Dammit!

777
01:30:43,695 --> 01:30:44,889
I love you too...

778
01:31:09,187 --> 01:31:10,484
come on...

779
01:31:10,688 --> 01:31:11,848
Now?

780
01:31:12,056 --> 01:31:14,718
Now what? Fifteen days in jail...

781
01:31:14,926 --> 01:31:15,654
What?

782
01:31:16,594 --> 01:31:20,394
Yeah... I stopped the train by pulling the chain...

783
01:31:23,301 --> 01:31:24,495
Why are you wearing this silly saree?

784
01:31:24,702 --> 01:31:25,361
I'd gone for Rishi's wedding...

785
01:31:25,603 --> 01:31:30,302
The foundation of a marriage
should only be love...

786
01:31:30,541 --> 01:31:31,565
And nothing else...

787
01:31:32,310 --> 01:31:36,110
because if the foundation
is wrong, relationships end...

788
01:31:36,481 --> 01:31:37,971
Like it happened with us...

789
01:31:38,649 --> 01:31:43,086
Years later, we found love... Happiness...

790
01:31:44,922 --> 01:31:46,787
But we just wish that...

791
01:31:47,625 --> 01:31:53,257
...the road to our destination didn't have
to be paved with broken hearts...
